title: So I just autofilled and now?
body: OK so i just got auto filled support.  Now It says its still active. Also I am in my promos. So isnt it protected?

replies.body: That sounds like a possible visual error.  You should be protected from auto-fill in your promotion series or if you auto-filled in your previous match.  Did you end up getting auto-filled?
